platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When it comes to getting the most out of your sleep, a tracker that can tell you much more than how many hours you’ve snoozed goes a long way. Rise does just that. It helps you understand how your activities impact your sleep health, and it focuses on sleep debt to help you close the gap between the sleep you need and the sleep you get.
This clever sleep tracker gives you a better understanding of how your activities impact your sleep health, and helps you close the gap between the sleep you need and the sleep you get.

Cette app de suivi intelligent du sommeil vous montre ce qui impacte la qualité de votre sommeil et comment combler le fossé entre la quantité de sommeil dont vous avez besoin et celle dont vous bénéficiez.
這款智能的睡眠追蹤工具可讓你更了解自己的日常活動如何影響睡眠健康，並助你逐漸縮窄所需睡眠與實際睡眠之間的差距。
這款優質的睡眠管理 App 會追蹤並分析你的日常作息，讓你更瞭解自己的睡眠品質，並幫助你縮小理想睡眠和實際睡眠的差距。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Keep track of your night’s rest for a fresher start to your day.
